CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Man standing with Eunice Cook wearing earrings, pearl necklace, and light colored dress with v-shaped bib and loop trim, posed in front of light colored curtains in interior with patterned carpeting for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends Inc.
